extends AmazonWebServiceRequest
implements java.io.Serializable, DryRunSupportedRequest<DescribeClassicLinkInstancesRequest>
    Container for the parameters to the DescribeClassicLinkInstances operation.

    Describes one or more of your linked EC2-Classic instances. This request only returns information about EC2-Classic instances linked to a VPC through ClassicLink; you cannot use this request to return information about other instances.

    See Also:
    AmazonEC2.describeClassicLinkInstances(DescribeClassicLinkInstancesRequest), Serialized Form
